Server validation rule of the table Country_Flag

Code preview of the table Country_Flag

USE DATABASECOUNTRYHL
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYS.SYSREFERENCES R JOIN SYS.SYSOBJECTS O ON (O.ID = R.CONSTID AND O.TYPE = 'F')
WHERE R.FKEYID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_FLAG') AND O.NAME = 'FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYFL_COUNTRY')
ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_FLAG
DROP CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYFL_COUNTRY
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSINDEXES
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_FLAG')
AND NAME = 'COUNTRYFLAG_FK'
AND INDID > 0
AND INDID < 255)
DROP INDEX COUNTRY_FLAG.COUNTRYFLAG_FK
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_FLAG
DROP CONSTRAINT PK_COUNTRY_FLAG
go

IF EXISTS (SELECT 1
FROM SYSOBJECTS
WHERE ID = OBJECT_ID('COUNTRY_FLAG')
AND TYPE = 'U')
DROP TABLE COUNTRY_FLAG
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: COUNTRY_FLAG */
/*==============================================================*/
CREATE TABLE COUNTRY_FLAG (
COF_ID INT IDENTITY,
COU_ID INT NOT NULL,
COF_FLAG VARBINARY(8000) NOT NULL
)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_FLAG
ADD CONSTRAINT PK_COUNTRY_FLAG PRIMARY KEY (COF_ID)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: COUNTRYFLAG_FK */
/*==============================================================*/




CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX COUNTRYFLAG_FK ON COUNTRY_FLAG (COU_ID ASC)
go

ALTER TABLE COUNTRY_FLAG
ADD CONSTRAINT FK_COUNTRY__COUNTRYFL_COUNTRY FOREIGN KEY (COU_ID)
REFERENCES COUNTRY (COU_ID)
go
